Information

Gadget Man (previously Stephen Fry: Gadget Man) is a British television series, which began airing on 19 November 2012 on Channel 4 and is presented by Richard Ayoade, who took over from the previous host, Stephen Fry, from the second series. Each episode presents a variety of innovative products related to the episode's theme. The series is filmed in and around The Lime House, a 1930s art deco converted water tower in Norton, Kent.
